title: Behind the numbers of Virginia Tech Baseball's climb up the Top 25 polls - VT hokiesports.com
content: Behind the numbers of Virginia Tech Baseball's climb up the Top 25 polls  VT hokiesports.com
description: Fresh off a series win over then-No. 2 Miami (Fla.), the Virginia Tech baseball team has skyrocketed up the D1Baseball.com Top 25 poll all the way to No. 8, the highest-ever ranking in program history.
